    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. While it runs well, the exterior shows expected signs of use, including some clear coat peeling on the hood and minor scuffs on the rear bumper. The interior is clean but has some wear on the driver's seat upholstery; however, all electronics and the air conditioning are fully functional. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
