    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine stepping into a time capsule where the world slows down and every curve of the bodywork catches the light like a polished jewel. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved masterpiece of automotive history, radiating a quiet confidence that only comes from a life of pampered luxury. From the supple, unblemished leather that still carries the scent of prestige to the silent, effortless purr of a heart that beats as strongly today as the moment it left the factory, this vehicle is an invitation to rediscover the joy of the open road. It is more than a purchase\u2014it is the acquisition of a legacy.",
      "price": 48500.0,
